 Assalamou Alaikum Md Sahadatunnobi

We invite you to renew your support for the Manitoba Islamic Association. O=
ur
records show your membership is currently inactive.

For just $30/year, your membership helps sustain our community initiatives =
and
gives you full access to MIA services.

Please note that because we are transitioning to a new platform, you will n=
eed
to re-submit your details during registration.




MEMBERSHIP BENEFITS=E2=9C=A8
=E2=9C=85 Discounts on MIA Gym & Kitchen rentals
=E2=9C=85 One-time discount on MIA School tuition
=E2=9C=85 Voting eligibility in the AGM (If member by August 1)
=E2=9C=85 Eligibility to run for the MIA Board (If member by April 1)


If you have already signed up or renewed your membership this year, or have
questions about your status, please contact the MIA office at=20
office@miaonline.org or 204-256-1347.

Jazakum Allahu Khairan for your continued support!

